%% Data Flow Diagram - OpenVINO Model Server (OVMS)
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant REST as OVMS REST Server<br/>rest_port/TCP HTTP
    participant gRPC as OVMS gRPC Server<br/>port/TCP gRPC
    participant Handler as HttpRestApiHandler
    participant KFS as KFSInferenceServiceImpl
    participant TFS as TFS PredictionServiceImpl
    participant V3 as processV3 Handler
    participant MP as MediaPipe Graph<br/>LLM Calculator
    participant MM as ModelManager
    participant OV as OpenVINO Runtime
    participant GenAI as OpenVINO GenAI<br/>Continuous Batching
    participant S3 as Cloud Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 1: KServe v2 REST Inference

    Client->>REST: POST /v2/models/{model}/infer<br/>HTTP plaintext, No Auth
    REST->>Handler: Route request
    Handler->>KFS: KServe v2 inference
    KFS->>MM: Get model instance
    MM->>OV: Execute inference
    OV-->>MM: Inference result
    MM-->>KFS: Prediction output
    KFS-->>Handler: Format response
    Handler-->>REST: JSON response
    REST-->>Client: HTTP 200 OK

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: gRPC Inference (TFS)

    Client->>gRPC: PredictionService.Predict<br/>gRPC plaintext, No Auth
    gRPC->>TFS: Route to TFS impl
    TFS->>MM: Get model instance
    MM->>OV: Execute inference
    OV-->>MM: Inference result
    MM-->>TFS: Prediction output
    TFS-->>gRPC: gRPC response
    gRPC-->>Client: Prediction response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: OpenAI Chat Completion (LLM)

    Client->>REST: POST /v3/chat/completions<br/>HTTP plaintext, Bearer API key
    REST->>Handler: Route to v3
    Handler->>Handler: isAuthorized()<br/>Verify API key
    Handler->>V3: processV3
    V3->>MP: MediaPipe Graph execution
    MP->>GenAI: Continuous batching<br/>Token generation
    GenAI-->>MP: Generated tokens (streaming)
    MP-->>V3: SSE stream or JSON
    V3-->>Handler: Response
    Handler-->>REST: SSE stream / JSON
    REST-->>Client: Server-Sent Events<br/>or JSON response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 4: Model Loading from Object Storage

    MM->>MM: Startup / config reload
    MM->>S3: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS 1.2+<br/>AWS IAM / GCP SA / Azure creds
    S3-->>MM: Model files
    MM->>OV: Load model into runtime
    OV-->>MM: Model ready
